<FIRST>u f PM-BoardofTrade Open   07-01 0351</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Board of Trade, Open,0363</SECOND>
<HEAD>Grain, Soybean Futures Open Higher</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
